Quickstrike sighed and shrugged again. There was no response even after 
yelling at Megatron. That didn't work, and he had learned never to yell at 
the boss.

He looked at Stingtra.

"Ah say we jus' go ahead. If we see somethin' we's can always tell Dark 
Mouse."
